WEBVTT

00:02.068 --> 00:04.921
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:04.921 --> 00:07.424
Here's something about
a show of impressionists

00:07.424 --> 00:08.925
coming to Boston this fall.

00:08.925 --> 00:10.343
Well, why wait?

00:10.343 --> 00:12.345
I do one that'll knock your socks off.

00:12.345 --> 00:15.131
He's talkin' about
French painters, doofus.

00:15.131 --> 00:16.466
Yeah? Well, so am I.

00:16.466 --> 00:18.468
Yeah, I do a great Cezanne.

00:18.468 --> 00:20.854
Get outta here. No, I do. Watch this.

00:20.854 --> 00:23.773
(French accent): Hosey,
posey, life is perfect.

00:23.773 --> 00:25.859
(as John Wayne): Hey, ya better smile

00:25.859 --> 00:27.861
when ya say that, Pilgrim.

00:27.861 --> 00:29.863
(as James Stewart): Now, now, now, now,

00:29.863 --> 00:31.865
just a-just a darned
second there, young fella.

00:31.865 --> 00:33.867
(all chuckling)

00:34.868 --> 00:37.370
Okay, okay, I got one. Watch this.

00:41.041 --> 00:42.542
(with country accent): Hey, fellers.

00:42.542 --> 00:45.045
I believe we might be
in for just a little rain

00:45.045 --> 00:46.913
before this day's over.

00:46.913 --> 00:48.631
Woody, who is that?

00:48.631 --> 00:51.801
It's Dwight Womack,
mayor of Hanover, Indiana.

00:54.587 --> 00:56.589
No, Woody, Woody, when
you do impressions,

00:56.589 --> 00:58.591
you gotta do impressions
of famous people.

00:58.591 --> 01:00.477
Well, if I could do somebody famous,

01:00.477 --> 01:01.978
why would I be doin' Dwight Womack?

01:01.978 --> 01:03.480
Yeah, good point.

01:03.480 --> 01:05.482
Yeah, he's got a point.

01:06.983 --> 01:10.854
(piano plays)

01:10.854 --> 01:13.323
? Making your way in the world today ?

01:13.323 --> 01:16.326
? Takes everything you've got ?

01:16.326 --> 01:19.329
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

01:19.329 --> 01:22.332
? Sure would help a lot ?

01:22.332 --> 01:27.587
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

01:27.587 --> 01:30.373
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:30.373 --> 01:35.378
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:35.378 --> 01:40.383
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:40.383 --> 01:42.385
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:42.385 --> 01:45.388
? Our troubles are all the same ?

01:45.388 --> 01:50.393
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

01:50.393 --> 01:53.396
? You want to go where people know ?

01:53.396 --> 01:55.398
? People are all the same ?

01:55.899 --> 02:00.403
? You want to go where
everybody knows your name. ?

